1. Create the Dockerfile
2. Import the necessary dependencies 
3. Import the java file
4. Build the image of the Dockerfile
	a. $ docker build -f Dockerfile -t demo/oracle-java:8 .

5. Build the java file 
	a. $ docker run --rm -v $PWD:/app -w /app demo/oracle-java:8 javac Main.java
6. Run the Java file
	a.  docker run --rm -v $PWD:/app -w /app demo/oracle-java:8 java Main
